Australian Regulator Amends Standards to Allow Covered Bonds

-- B y   E d w a r d   J o h n s o n
-- 
2011-10-20T03:35:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/australian-regulator-amends-standards-to-allow-covered-bonds.html
The  Australian Prudential Regulation
Authority  said it amended standards to allow local banks to
issue covered bonds, after parliament passed legislation last
week authorizing sales of the asset-backed securities.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Edward Johnson at 
 ejohnson28@bloomberg.net  